'''Noureddin Ziad Bani Attiah''' ({{langx|ar|نُور الدِّين زِيَاد بَنِي عَطِيَّة}}; born 25 January 1993) is a [[Jordan]]ian [[football (soccer)|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Al-Faisaly SC (Amman)|Al-Faisaly]] and the [[Jordan national football team|Jordan national team]].

